SUMMARY:Build Dance Skills at Bachata Locura - Bachata Bootcamp and Social
DESCRIPTION:Bachata Locura: Midnight in Spring Edition~ Bachata Bootcamp and Social Dance Event.\n\n\nJoin us March 22nd at Yuengling Draft Haus💫 \n➡️ A special collaboration between ODT x RELPRO Dance Promotions x The Dance Factory – Tampa brings together education\, connection\, and a high-energy social to fulfill all your dance needs🥳 \n🌷Schedule:🕐 1:30–3:30 PM — Bachata Musicality Bootcamp (with Albina & Isaac – cover includes the social + pre-social class)🕓 4:00–5:00 PM — Pre-Social Class (with Albina & Isaac – included in social cover)💃🏼 4:00–9:00 PM — Bachata Locura Social \n🌸 Theme: Midnight SpringThink: florals\, linen\, pastels 🌺🌌 \n🎟 Early Bird tickets are LIVE now – ends March 14th! Prices increase after. Ticket link in bio‼️ \nCome early. Train well. Dance hard.This is Bachata Locura 🔥 \n#BachataLocura #MidnightSpring #BachataBootcamp #Musicality #TampaDance #LatinDance
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/build-dance-skills-at-bachata-locura-bachata-bootcamp-and-social-2-2/
LOCATION:Yuengling Draft Haus & Kitchen\, 11109 North 30th Street\, Tampa\, FL 33612\, Tampa\, FL\, 33612\, US
CATEGORIES:Tampa
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/302407_image.png
END:VEVENT
