SUMMARY:Cuban Sundays at The Dark Horse Stables
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for Cuban Sundays at The Dark Horse Stables!\nWe’re turning up the heat with two amazing rooms full of dancing\, music\, and good vib\n\n\nGet ready for Cuban Sundays at The Dark Horse Stables! \nWe’re turning up the heat with two amazing rooms full of dancing\, music\, and good vibes! \nLeft Room \n💃 4:00 PM – 6:00 PM: Dance it out with the amazing Maikel Mota \n🎶 6:00 PM – 11:00 PM: Feel the groove as DJ Petit spins the best of Kizomba \nRight Room \n🔥 4:00 PM – 11:00 PM: Keep the party going all night with DJ Ricafed and Johnny Gee \nPlus\, everyone joining the event gets a special discount to dine at any restaurant in The Dark Horse. \nCome dance\, eat\, and celebrate Cuban style!
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/cuban-sundays-at-the-dark-horse-stables/2026-03-22/
