SUMMARY:Salsa and Bachata Dancing at Moonshine Beach in Pacific Beach
DESCRIPTION:We are excited to announce we are back for dancing at Moonshine Beach\nSunday party Salsa and Bachata dancing at Moonshine Beach in Pacific Beach San Diego\n4:30-9pm \nArrive early with friends\n4:30pm Salsa lesson\nAll levels welcome\, no partner needed \nDancing Salsa & Bachata all night\nwith DJ Mo Lyon \nHuge dance floor\, amazing venue\, the entire space has wood floors.\n21+\n$15 cover at entrance\nMake sure to invite and share with your friends\nDefinitely one of the best places to dance in SD
