SUMMARY:Rooftop Salsa & Bachata Social
DESCRIPTION:Atlanta’s Premiere Rooftop Salsa & Bachata Social\n📍 Reverb Hotel Atlanta | Hosted by Fuego Y Hielo Dance Company\n🗓️ Every 4th Sunday of the month\n🕓 4:30PM – 9:30PM | 💃 $20 Admission\nThis is your chance to dance\, vibe\, and unwind at Atlanta’s most stunning rooftop destination.\n✨ What to Expect:\n🔹 4:30PM – Complimentary Salsa or Bachata Class — great for beginners or anyone looking to refine their steps.\n🔹 5:30PM–9:30PM – Rooftop social dancing with the best Salsa & Bachata DJs in the city.\n🍹 Full Bar & Food Available\nEnjoy tasty bites and refreshing cocktails all evening.\n🚗 PARKING OPTIONS:\n• Recommended: Park in Castleberry Hill and take a short scenic walk to the venue.\n• On-Site: Reverb Hotel offers $25 parking (includes a drink ticket).\n📆 Mark Your Calendars!\nReverb & Vibe will now be a monthly tradition — happening every 4th Sunday!\n🔥 Come for the views. ❄️ Stay for the vibes.\nLet the music move you at The R&V Social.
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/rooftop-salsa-bachata-social/2026-03-22/
LOCATION:Reverb Hotel Atlanta\, 89 Centennial Olympic Park\, Atlanta\, GA\, 30313\, United States
CATEGORIES:Atlanta
END:VEVENT
