SUMMARY:Salsa Bachata Havana Nights @ La Industria
DESCRIPTION:Every Sunday Salsa ATL & D4F Presents..\nHavana Nights ATL @ La Industria Mexican Grill\nLatin Night in Gwinnett\n– NO COVER CHARGE FOR PARTY \nSalsa & Bachata Lesson s + Tacos & Mexican Food\n+\nLatin dancing \n—\n5:30pm – 7:30pm Salsa & Bachata lesson \nBeginner & Beyond Basic\n— 7:30pm – 12am Best of Salsa\, Bachata\, Merengue & more\n— Drink & Food Specials\n— REMINDER NO OUTSIDE FOOD OR DRINKS ALLOWED —\n— Kitchen is Open Late \nJoin us each & every Sunday learn some cool Salsa\n& Bachata moves. Grab some delicious Mexican\nFood & stay for the best mix of Salsa\, Bachata\,\nMerengue & more.\nBe sure to bring your appetite along with your\ndance shoes. Delicious Tacos\, Enchiladas & much more! \nWhere:\nLa Industria Mexican Grill\n( Far Right of Shopping Center) \n3466 Holcomb Bridge Rd \,\nPeachtree Corners\, GA 30092\n(770) 802 8133\n– directions\n770 855 4396 – questions about event \nSchedule:\nREMINDER NO OUTSIDE FOOD OR DRINKS ALLOWED \n— 5:30pm 7:30pm Salsa & Bachata lesson – $30/person in adv\n— 7:30pm – 12midnight\nBest of Salsa\, Bachata \nNo Cover charge for Party \nGo to the link below to pay for\nDance lesson in adv:\nhttps://HavanaNightsAtlanta.Eventbee.com \nQuestions about the Party\n(770) 802 8133 – directions or to make reservations\n770 855 4396 – questions about event
