SUMMARY:Vinyl Matinee Sundays
DESCRIPTION:A great lineup of powerhouse UK djs for your dancing pleasure!\nJoin a fun-filled salsa early evening with the finest tunes!\n***\nSunday early evening with quality salsa on vinyl on the very spacious and fully air-conditioned McNamara Hall on the London Irish Centre\, Camden. Looking forward to dancing with you and sharing the joy of salsa!\nGreat variety of drinks\, best Guinness in town and hot and cold beverages to accompany your Sunday salsa dose!\nPLEASE NOTE:\n– Bring your own water bottle for refill (the venue will be providing a plastic cup per person for reuse on the night to minimise single-usage cups)\n– We have over-the-shoe socks that make dancing on the wood floor very smooth and spinning very easy. You can try them at the door and if you like how they feel\, purchase for £2. They protect your dance shoes and also make any hard floor easy to spin on. Wash and use over and over again\nVENUE:\nThe London Irish Centre\,\n50-52 Camden Square\,\nLondon\, NW1 9XB
