DESCRIPTION:Join us each and every Sunday at Dovercourt House\, where we are giving you the best of Salsa y Bachata. \nDate and Time: Sunday 5:30pm to 11pm \nDance Lessons at 6pm \nMulti Levels Salsa Lessons at 6pm by UnitedSalseros (beginner\, Intermediate\, Advance)\nKizomba Lesson by Babs and Nyemu at 7pm\nSocial Dancing: 3 Rooms\, 3 DJs \nSalsa Music by DJ Timber (First Floor) 7pm – 11pm \nBachata Music by DJ Mondo (3rd Floor) 7pm – 11pm \nKizomba Lesson by DJ Amano (2nd floor) 8pm – 11pm \nCover – Fee: $15 ($5 discount with Friday unbroken wristband or otherwise pre-register on Friday) \nAddress: 805 Dovercourt Rd.\, Toronto (walking distance from Ossington Subway Station) \n— 𝐒𝐭𝐫𝐞𝐞𝐭 𝐏𝐚𝐫𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐏𝐚𝐢𝐝 𝐏𝐚𝐫𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐠 — You can park on Dovercourt Rd until Midnight\, you can park on Bloor st after midnight without restriction. There are couple of Paid parking spaces near our venue: \n1022 Bloor St W\n1048 Bloor St W\n9 Salem Ave (Green P)\n7 Bartlett Ave (CarPark)\n745 Ossington Ave (Green P)
