SUMMARY:Sunday Social in Tigard
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the SUNDAY SOCIAL in beautiful downtown Tigard! A great place to meet people\, get exercise and have fun dancing! \nAre you new to dancing? Don’t worry\, there is a beginner lesson and plenty of people that will help you learn throughout the night! \nCome join us for an amazing time! 7:00PM – 10:00PM*\n7:00-7:30PM BEGINNING Bachata lesson\nNo partner or experience needed. We rotate in the lesson.\nFollowed by DJ’d Salsa & Bachata mix till 10:00PM\n*(6:00PM – 9:00PM in the Winter) – Please check the Shawn Gardner website for updates. \n7:00-7:30PM BALLROOM lesson\n7:30-10:00PM DJ’d Ballroom music in our Main Room \nOPEN TO SINGLES & COUPLES\nOPEN TO ALL AGES\nBeer\, Wine & Cider available this evening\nALL inclusive environment\nOpen to the Public!\nCover $10/ person\nOr included in Membership. Ask about Membership options at our front desk!\nSee you all there!
